This directory vendors the satel_integra2 protocol client, bundled with Satel
Link because the version providing 0xEE device discovery and zone bypass is not
published on PyPI.

Origin and credit (MIT-licensed at the root):

  wasilukm/satel_integra2        original, published on PyPI (MIT)
    -> sjauquet/satel_integra2   fork
    -> alessioburgassi/satel_integra2   fork (added discovery/bypass)
    -> barloew/satel_integra2    fork used here

The upstream root project is MIT-licensed. This vendored copy is redistributed
under those terms; see the LICENSE file in this directory. Only the runtime
client modules are vendored (satel_integra.py, encryption.py, __init__.py); the
CLI and tests are omitted.
